♪Yet stand before my eyes♪

30
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,800
I hate you.

31
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:40,224
♪If you would meet me face to face♪

32
00:04:40,224 --> 00:04:44,000
♪I'd die without a single regret♪

33
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:49,984
♪You're the distant star♪

34
