♪For your tears and embrace♪

37
00:05:02,016 --> 00:05:04,288
♪I'll brave all the blizzards♪

38
00:05:04,288 --> 00:05:08,480
♪To walk with you♪

39
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:11,840
♪Butterflies climb mountains for love♪

40
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:14,208
♪Perish before the flowers♪

41
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,544
Yunqing.

42
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:23,800
I have considered ending this life.

43
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:32,040
But for our child,

44
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,720
I'll keep living well.

45
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,920
I'll spare no effort

46
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:46,160
to find your killer.

47
00:05:47,060 --> 00:05:49,952
♪Our eyes met across the mortal world♪

48
