♪Butterflies climb mountains for love♪

206
00:16:39,585 --> 00:16:41,921
♪Perish before the flowers♪

207
00:16:42,433 --> 00:16:47,937
♪You seem so distant,
yet right before my eyes♪

208
00:16:48,577 --> 00:16:50,753
♪A game of chess, a fate of strife♪

209
00:16:50,753 --> 00:16:53,985
♪I dream of standing
with you, side by side♪

210
00:16:54,209 --> 00:16:55,969
♪If you would meet me face to face♪

211
00:16:55,969 --> 00:16:59,649
♪I'd die without a single regret♪

212
